## chart goal-contract Lofty Goal Contract
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  current["current_reality: web FrankenTerm shell works, TUI thought rail exists, clawgs v2 cues flow into swimmers, shared operator pressure feeds Trogdor atlas"]
  gaps["conditional_followup: post-commit reality check only if a commit is authorized"]
  goal["lofty_end_goal: web-only Trogdor mode turns live sessions into a pressure-aware operator loop without new backend nouns"]
  bars["non_negotiable_quality_bars: reuse contracts, TUI parity, web proof, hardening loop, docs, post-commit reality check"]
  scope["out_of_scope: new Trogdor schema, raw transcript parser in swimmers, renamed villager_intent or burninate_command models"]
  proof["proof_of_slice_done: action cues visible end-to-end, web atlas uses Rust operator_pressure model, live marker smoke passes, tests pass"]

  current --> gaps --> goal --> bars --> proof
  scope -. excluded .-> goal

  classDef current fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#0c4a6e,stroke-width:2px
  classDef gap fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#7f1d1d,stroke-width:2px
  classDef goal fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#3b0764,stroke-width:2px
  classDef proof fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:2px
  class current current
  class gaps,scope gap
  class goal,bars goal
  class proof proof
```

## chart reality-gap Current Reality and Gap Evidence
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  docs["Docs and vision"] --> vision["OK: agent observability and local-first web control surface are real project intent"]
  wiki["Wiki sweep"] --> essence["OK: Trogdor means attention race plus pause quality, not raw game mechanics"]
  web["src/web"] --> shell["OK: web shell, FrankenTerm assets, selection follow, create, search, send, config, Mermaid sheets exist"]
  tui["src/bin/swimmers_tui"] --> rail["OK: thought rail has needs-input, batch send, launch, commit, Mermaid, plans"]
  clawgs["../clawgs"] --> cues["OK: clawgs.emit.v2 action_cues are canonical deterministic facts"]
  tests["Verification"] --> unit["OK: Rust library, metamorphic, JS surface, and live web smoke tests passed"]
  tests --> smoke["OK: scripts/test-web-live-terminal.sh proves marker round trip"]
  protocol["src/thought/protocol.rs and src/types.rs"] --> drop["OK: swimmers carries clawgs-style action_cues into SessionSummary and thought payloads"]
  plan["Planning state"] --> missing["OK: docs/TROGDOR_WEB_WORKGRAPH.md records completed work and deferred scope"]
  game["Trogdor mode"] --> noimpl["OK: web atlas and hover speed-reader vertical slice exists"]
  game --> sharedgap["OK: pressure derivation moved to src/operator_pressure.rs and /v1/operator-pressure"]
  game --> actions["OK: hover panel can send, batch-send, launch, open Mermaid, and launch commit Codex"]
  game --> plans["OK: Mermaid sheet exposes existing plan_files via /v1/sessions/{id}/plan-file"]
  game --> visual["OK: atlas includes burninate banner, repo structures, burninating pressure rows, and agent glyphs"]
  game --> operator_doc["OK: docs/TROGDOR_WEB.md explains controls and reuse contract"]

  classDef ok fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:2px
  classDef med fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:2px
  classDef high fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#7f1d1d,stroke-width:2px
  classDef neutral fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
  class docs,wiki,web,tui,clawgs,tests,protocol,plan,game neutral
  class vision,essence,shell,rail,cues,unit,smoke,drop,noimpl,sharedgap,actions,plans,visual,operator_doc,missing ok
```

## chart routing Planning and Skill Routing
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  start["Start from current reality"]
  smart["smart goal tracker"]
  wiki["wiki: Trogdor essence and quality gates"]
  bvc["build-vs-clone: reuse swimmers and clawgs"]
  describe{"Are pass/fail criteria sharp enough?"}
  domain{"Does this require new cross-repo domain ownership?"}
  spec["describe: define pressure view pass/fail cases"]
  direct["direct swimmers implementation"]
  clawgsroute["clawgs change only if existing action_cues are insufficient"]
  workgraph["beads or WORKGRAPH after criteria are sharp"]
  mmdx["mmdx tracker and proof gates"]

  start --> smart --> wiki --> bvc --> describe
  describe -->|no| spec --> workgraph
  describe -->|yes| domain
  domain -->|no| direct --> workgraph
  domain -->|yes| clawgsroute --> workgraph
  workgraph --> mmdx

  classDef decision fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#3b0764,stroke-width:2px
  classDef action fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
  classDef proof fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:2px
  class describe,domain decision
  class start,smart,wiki,bvc,spec,direct,clawgsroute,workgraph action
  class mmdx proof
```

